;Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=============================================================Main
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 幸虧沒出現傷者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 為防止恐慌擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要準備好對外發表的聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 實際上這並不是地震...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂雜開放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.27,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,436)}<Poltergeist>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是亂雜開放 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你救了我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷就最好不過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在測量這裡發生的AIM擴散力場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在MAR 還能自在地探查力場的異常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不...那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得你們採取對策太神速了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員 第一七七支部的白井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 看來一七七支部人才濟濟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於RSPK和AIM擴散力場的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RSPK是有人故意向AIM擴散力場進行干涉而造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其同時多發就會引起亂雜開放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在聯合會議上你挑明了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員也能幫你們推斷出可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是警備員的管轄範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如我在會議上說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望風紀委員能專注在應對謠言傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有日常的安全對策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對AIM擴散力場進行干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這樣做的 還另有其人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另有其人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪她們去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行啊 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍監差不多要巡房了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上沒事 能回宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼從剛才開始就埋頭查東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想御手事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼到現在還查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺跟這次亂雜開放事件很像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到頭來不也是利用AIM擴散力場的犯罪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我也會不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不過眼的話 到時就再來妨礙我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懷疑這次的事件是不是又跟木山有關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了一件關鍵的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山春生正待在第十七學區的特殊拘留所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她那樣的重犯 不可能跑得出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的也對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我還有件事情放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是春上當時的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 她當時好像就在跟不在場的某人在對話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次亂雜開放事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是有人對AIM擴散力場進行干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 恐怕是能力者幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也不願意往這方面想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別粘我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 那怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上可是才剛剛轉學過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 春上以前住的第十九學區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是吵鬧靈的多發地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天這麼說過啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十九學區最近沒有發生亂雜開放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過相對地 我們第七學區...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是偶然啦 偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼乖巧的女孩子 怎麼可能跟亂雜開放有關呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這人不能太多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪固法學姐那個電話...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...固法學姐 貴安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事起碼也給我報個平安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個...呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你啊...總是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 讓你一直陪著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客氣啥啊 錯又不在你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的室友 就是我的摯友候補啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺今天都是在麻煩你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天「也」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過春上還真是嚇了我一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然完全不記得地震的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就跟醫生說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計稍微有點休克狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然煙花大會出大事了 還好大家都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 你要好好好照顧春上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 佐天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎樣 要不要喝點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是...給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己 好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知會不會又惹大家討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 春上還有我跟著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 佐天剛才買了好東西來看望你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是熊本西瓜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天說 在學園都市栽培的西瓜都不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是初春 還是佐天 大家都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我一個人的話 根本一事無成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會傻等...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很討厭那樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想去改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 能改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是托大家的福 才當上了風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上身邊 也有大家跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 一定能改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的...能改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我敢打包票
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 盡情吃 打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然公園？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟春上兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾 怎麼不叫上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 我都不知道你今天不用值班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想偶爾吸吸負...離子也不錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你是不是哮喘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣喘得那麼粗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很粗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 難得過來玩 被放鴿子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是來玩的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 要不要買些冰涼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要冷面 什錦炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸薯條 小皿炒烏冬 還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胃口真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 春卷也不錯 生的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 會不會太多了點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡還是有點不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不過我們也是為了消除春上嫌疑...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 能力是Telepathy 精神感應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是異能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.89,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(467,438)}<Level 2>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說基本上還沒到能應用的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 春上跟亂雜開放沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只是我們杞人憂天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:55.23,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,<位於特定波長底下時為例外 會發揮出等級以上的能力>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風吹得好舒服～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方吃壽司卷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道分外地好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春對我說的那番話 我一直都在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一定能改變的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須向你說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在找一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她關係一直都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一天 就分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾經跟我約定過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說一定能再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 光是等是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得主動去找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我等待的時候 她現在也...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 一起去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事 怎麼這麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了 春上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那可是意外地好吃 下次我買過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一學區 自然公園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了大規模的亂雜開放？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然公園？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是初春她們在的公園嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.06,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(401,10)}{\bord0\shad0}{\fad(150,0)}{\fscx92}#21{\fscx98\b0} {\1c&H4D81DF}聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受害狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷者72名 其中有18名重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前沒有出現死者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續進行救助作業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確跟真正的地震沒有區別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽話 你也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 我是風紀委員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我力所能及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是上次那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 有沒受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 讓你們特意過來看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如大家所見 只是輕微擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了這點傷沒大礙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可擔心了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 竟然接連遇到兩次亂雜開放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟春上運氣也實在太...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 春上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她先被救助隊轉移了 估計在某處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不用擔心 她沒受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 不過沒受傷就最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春 發生亂雜開放之前那段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上有沒有出現什麼奇怪狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是指像上次煙花大會那樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然春上只是異能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.17,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(511,438)}<Level 2>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是個有點奇怪的精神感應者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.97,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(558,436)}<Telepath>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果出現了上次那樣的可疑舉動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要查她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是在懷疑春上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也 也不是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井 你好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上才剛轉學過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不安 還很依賴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你卻...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你卻懷疑她！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春 先冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 初春 黑子她並不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神感應者成為AIM擴散力場的干涉者 也並非沒可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷斯蒂娜小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡看來收納不下更多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就轉移去十五學區的緊急醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那至少需要大能力者以上的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:56.97,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(456,438)}<Level 4>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不說是相當稀有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異能力者嘛 這個可能性基本上是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.37,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(244,438)}<Level 2>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小心起見 還是先仔細調查一下為好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上衿衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一名遇災者送去總部的研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我調一臺車到正門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要認為這是證明她的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 我們有專業的工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 在醫院要保持安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 初春
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要西瓜紅茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦 嗓子都乾死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 黑子也喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 春上她怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要著急 結果出來還需一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這裡完全不像是研究所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還很有品味來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個女人還去搞災害救助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果喜歡這種純真的東西 一般人都會覺得意外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是我的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 再自我介紹一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先進狀況救助隊 附屬研究所所長 特雷斯蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所長？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你是MAR的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究所所長 呃...還有什麼名堂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 我還不知道白井同學以外的人的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是御坂美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是常盤臺那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能在這種地方見到超電磁砲 真是榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫佐天淚子 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是常盤臺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是柵川初中的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是御坂同學的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也是有相當水平的能力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個...我嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說了 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紀委員 第一七七支部 初春飾利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 那就是跟白井...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上應該不是干涉者...不是犯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要試試看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都喜歡 不過硬要說的話 黃色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃色是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到 到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 是個好兆頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不知道本小姐乃常盤臺的婚後光子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都解釋過很多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於大能力者引發亂雜開放的資料很少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:21.78,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(291,438)}<Level 4>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要多做點檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有不舒服的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛卡迪莉娜也在等著我回...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井 御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快制住她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果出來了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 她不是干涉者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的確是Level 2的精神感應者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是專門接收信息的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法自身發出思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過數據庫上記載的資料說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於特定波長底下時為例外 會發揮出等級以上的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井 你還這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從檢查結果上來看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她接收的來源方很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那個來源方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠無視距離和障礙物 確確實實地捕捉到思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 她不可能對AIM擴散力場進行干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 照你這樣說的話 誰才是真正的干涉者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...又
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 都沒事了 你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這是我和那個朋友的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個朋友 就是你在找的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能聽見 她的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是精神感應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是時不時聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 一聽到那聲音 就會發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 當時也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面放著什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫枝先絆理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是當時那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識絆理？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是...被拋棄者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.84,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,438)}<Child Error>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到春上竟然是被拋棄者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:39.91,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\shad0\bord1.5\an9}{\1c&H4D81DF}{\fscx92}#22{\fscx98}  Level 6
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:39.91,*title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\shad0\bord1.5\an9}{\1c&H4D81DF\fs14}<以非神之身到達天上意思者>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子和初春還在鬧彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這裡就由我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 是你？！


